---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Cameron's Coffee — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Cameron's Coffee scaled from 0 to 5 robotic palletizers in 12 months with Formic's Robots-as-a-Service model — over 1 million pounds of coffee palletized, zero capital outlay."
  ogTitle="Cameron's Coffee — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="0 to 5 systems in 12 months · 1M+ lbs palletized · zero CapEx"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/camerons-coffee" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Cameron's Coffee
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Cameron's Coffee</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">Cameron's Coffee Hits Automation "Easy Button", Scaling from 0 to 5 Systems in 12 Months</h1>
    <p class="lede">Cameron's Coffee went from zero robots to five palletizers in twelve months — over a million pounds of coffee palletized, with no capital outlay and no in-house robotics team to build.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/camerons-coffee-hero.jpg" alt="Cameron's Coffee and Formic — robotic palletizing partnership" style="object-fit:contain;background:var(--black);padding:5%"/>
      <span class="dv-cap">Cameron's Coffee · Shakopee, MN</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Founded</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">1978</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Shakopee, MN</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Coffee roasting & packaging</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Daily output</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">50,000+ lbs/day</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Formic systems</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">5 palletizers</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>Scaling fast, with <em>no room for downtime</em>.</h2>
      <p>Roasting since 1978, Cameron's grew from a small-batch roastery into an operation producing over 50,000 lbs of coffee a day across three shifts at its Shakopee, Minnesota plant — shipping to Target, Walmart, Cub Foods and more. As demand climbed, manual end-of-line stacking became the constraint: hard to staff, hard to keep reliable, and a safety risk. The team had no prior robotics experience and saw automation as expensive, uncertain, and risky against competing growth projects.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>50,000+ lbs of coffee per day across three shifts</li>
        <li>Manual stacking hard to staff and keep reliable</li>
        <li>No prior robotics experience; capital tied up in growth</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Cameron-Cobot-Palletizing.jpg" alt="Cameron's Coffee cobot palletizing cell at end of line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">End-of-line palletizing</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Robotic palletizer stacking finished cases" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Pay-for-productivity · RaaS</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Robots-as-a-Service, <em>not a capital project</em>.</h2>
      <p>Formic's Robots-as-a-Service model let Cameron's add automation simply and repeatably — full system design and deployment, committed uptime and performance, ongoing maintenance and upgrades, all for an hourly usage rate with zero capital investment. They started with the manual stacking task for its impact on efficiency, safety, and reliability, then lined up more end-of-line and upstream case-packing opportunities from Formic's 40+ pre-vetted solutions.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Zero capital investment — pay an hourly usage rate</li>
        <li>Committed uptime, maintenance, and upgrades included</li>
        <li>40+ pre-vetted solutions to scale into</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"Formic removes all the anxiety of a traditional equipment purchase. We like that they provide the entire solution, including committed uptime and service."</blockquote>
      <cite>Adam Bragg · Technical Director, Cameron's Coffee Shakopee Plant</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Results</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">Zero to five systems. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Twelve months.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">5</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Systems deployed</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">12</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Months to scale</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">1M+</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Lbs palletized</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Find your <em>easy button</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
